SetInCountry: Egypt
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: "H\xE9l\xE8ne  Bourque"
AuthorCountry: Canada
Text: "Nathalia is a young med student who has a bright future ahead of her, if she\
  \ follows the very detailed and thought out plan her parents have set up for her.\
  \ \n\nWhat they don\u2019t know is that Nathalia is part of a secret community,\
  \ a community of adventure seeking, thrill runners and travel junkies. This community\
  \ is like her family, where she is free to day dream about the fantasy lands she\
  \ wants to go and visit. Since her entering this community she\u2019s been given\
  \ many responsibilities that have sometimes proven difficult to keep up with, given\
  \ that she\u2019s a 4th year med student. \nHowever she is determined to make this\
  \ work. She knows all her hard work will pay off; however for Nathalia it\u2019\
  s not the reward of graduating from med school that excites her but the rewards\
  \ that will come from being apart of such a well rounded group of people who in\
  \ the end all have the same goal. \n\nMet with challenges and many obstacles Nathalia\
  \ never once gives up, although tempted to more then once. Fellow her adventure\
  \ and find out what this secret community is all about. \n\nWhat it this community?!\
  \ \nWhat adventures do they embark on?! \nDoes she follow the plan her parents have\
  \ written out for her or will she give in the who passion and desires ? \nTurn the\
  \ page to find out"
